Structural Divergence Analysis

Maria Laura Marcos, Julian Echave

Introduction

In this case we studied the az family. We used as reference for the ENM the protein with pdb code 1bxva. We simulated 10 mutants of this reference for each protein of the family. The az family is of the type beta and consists of the following proteins:
